      "name": "02 - Branches",
      "description": "Endpoints for managing branches within a franchise.\n\nA **branch** is a physical location (e.g. a restaurant outlet) that always belongs to exactly one franchise. Branch routes are nested under their parent franchise: `/api/v1/franchises/{franchiseId}/branches`.\n\n> **Prerequisite:** run **01 - Create Franchise** first so that `{{franchiseId}}` is set.",
