              "path": ["api", "v1", "franchises", "{{franchiseId}}", "branches"]
            },
            "description": "Creates a new branch under the franchise identified by `{{franchiseId}}`.\n\nThe server generates a UUID v7 as the branch `id`. The `id` is captured automatically by the test script and stored in the `{{branchId}}` collection variable.\n\n**Path parameters:**\n| Parameter | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `franchiseId` | UUID of the parent franchise |\n\n**Validation rules:**\n- `name` must be present and non-blank; otherwise the server returns `500`.\n\n**Example request body:**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Downtown Branch\"\n}\n```\n\n**Example response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"018f2c3d-4e5f-7a6b-b7c8-d9e0f1a2b3c4\",\n  \"name\": \"Downtown Branch\"\n}\n```"
